tly</strong><br><span style=\"color: #666; font-size: 14px;\">Connect with sellers in real-time</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;\">\n      <a href=\"https://mamvibe.com/create\" style=\"background: #e91e8c; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">Create Your First Listing</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #aaa; font-size: 12px;\">&copy; 2026 MamVibe. All rights reserved.</div>\n</div>",
